title: LCD Soundsystem Bonnaroo 2016
description:
I ripped the audio from a 720p stream (~160k AAC audio), preserved bitrate to the best of my ability, cut up, touched up, tagged, and uploaded

please enjoy/share/download/reupload/seed/sendeverywhere

I'm not looking for a buck or recognition or anything, this was easily one of the best nights of my life and I just want to do what I can to help share the love with others :D


also let me know if you hear any bugs/funkyness I need to correct!!
